3. Informing ODL of any job opportunities relevant for the programme.
4. Helping ODL in identifying the most relevant profile for a job description from the placement registered
students.
5. Suggesting companies to tie-up with the ODL Placement Cell and assist recruiters and DL office in providing
seamless recruitment process.
